title: We have £500,000 to help convert your empty property into new homes (Lewisham London Borough ...
text: ( Source : Lewisham London Borough Council ) Lewisham Council has won £ 500 , 000 from the Greater London Authority ( GLA ) to help turn empty property into homes and is looking for landlords, builders and businesses to come forward with proposals.
